high_descs: Turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Take the mug out of the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the mug on the bottom shelf of the fridge. Wait a moment and then take it out.
Turn left and walk back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug in the coffee maker where it was before.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the mug from where it sits under a coffee pot.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge for a little bit before retrieving it again.
Return to the toaster are and face the coffee pot.
Return the mug to where you found it.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug under the coffee pot.

high_descs: Go left towards the stove and then turn right and face the coffee maker.
Pick up the white mug from under the coffee maker.
Go right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and pick the mug up again and shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room and then go right to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Put the mug down under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left, proceed to stove.  Turn right, proceed to counter with coffee maker and toaster.
Remove mug from coffee maker.
Move right, proceed to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place mug on second shelf down, close refrigerator.  Wait five seconds.  Open refrigerator door, remove mug, close refrigerator door.
Turn around, proceed to stove.  Turn right, proceed to counter.
Place mug on coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Cool mug and return to coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup from the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk towards the fridge.
Place the cup on the second shelf inside the fridge, wait for a period before taking the cup out of the fridge.
Turn around and walk towards the coffee maker.
Place the cup on to the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To cool down the coffee mug

high_descs: Go ahead and veer left to the coffee maker.
Take the mug out of the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge on the bottom shelf. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out.
Turn around and walk back to the coffee maker on the counter.
Replace the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.
